DESCRIPTION:Description   Overview Join the Washington State Department of 
	Enterprise Services for a conversation on state contracting practices and 
	opportunities.    On the third Thursday of the month\, the Washington Stat
	e Department of Enterprise Services \\(DES\\) facilitates an interactive c
	onversation with state procurement professionals who can provide informati
	on and insight on how to do business with the state.  Join us for this vir
	tual event where we will discuss a variety of topics\, including:  Introd
	uction to state contracting  How to find upcoming contracting opportuniti
	es  Where to get technical assistance  Where to find additional training
	 And\, of course\, provide time and opportunity for questions and answers.
	  Who: Small\, Diverse\, and Veteran-Owned Businesses  Where: This will be
	 a live event hosted on Microsoft Teams. A Microsoft Teams link will be se
	nt out before the event. For additional information on how to access Micro
	soft Teams go to:   Accessibility Individuals with disabilities are encour
	aged to attend events sponsored by the Washington State Department of Ente
	rprise Services. If you require accommodations to participate in this even
	t\, don't hesitate to contact despieprogram@des.wa.gov.\n\nhttps://seatoda
	y.6amcity.com/events/#/details/state-contracting-opportunities-open-house/
	17486823/2026-03-19T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
